{"tid":1101824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三上悠亞也懂「老司機」！挺G奶自爆在家愛全裸","createTime":"2019-04-11T09:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T12:06:58.000Z","uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2e3009cbcf2d6311540a94e3b5972afa06514c6a","tid":1101824,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:47:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ay95iv-vGlE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fay95iv-vGlE&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUhZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=55475d95\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ay95iv-vGlE</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E90Z3ie.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE90Z3ie.png&h=08e2d122&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本AV天后三上悠亞今出席2019「TRE台北國際成人展」記者會，下午她身穿貼身白色小洋裝性感亮相，G奶更顯波濤洶湧，比出愛心手勢笑說要「收藏台灣粉絲的愛」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ciQWk48.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FciQWk48.png&h=ab503ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RGeLYRP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRGeLYRP.png&h=0e988381&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G46RUqb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG46RUqb.png&h=3a7aac13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於夏天將至，她也透露消暑秘訣就是在家時會「全裸」，享受無拘無束的感覺。記者會上她現場揮毫寫下「老司機」3個字，嬌羞表示聽說「老司機」這個詞在網路上有經驗老道、技術熟練的意思，因為第一次參加TRE台北國際成人展，心情上非常期待也很緊張，希望曾參與過成人展的粉絲們能夠帶領更多人來參與這次的盛會，特別學了這3個字答謝台灣粉絲的厚愛。此外，2019「TRE 台北國際成人展」將於8月2號至8月4號在新北工商展<br />\n覽館舉行。"},{"pid":"3b5e37af7d84b915f983a38835518f7e51b3765b","tid":1101824,"uid":49197,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:50:10.000Z","msg":"一般貨色"},{"pid":"e20d4202130b45acd142c42a248b3b576b6e923d","tid":1101824,"uid":838,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:51:23.000Z","msg":"鬼有G咩"},{"pid":"ba4336a478ce6c8e00273cfeeff57fa43d799291","tid":1101824,"uid":2757,"